TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: this lookup is to get data from SAS_HBISP_CANADA
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SAS_HBISP_CANADA

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT LTRIM(RTRIM(Style_group)) as Style_group, LTRIM(RTRIM(SBU)) as SBU, LTRIM(RTRIM(Customer)) as Customer, LTRIM(RTRIM(Currency)) as Currency FROM dbo.SAS_HBISP_CANADA with ( nolock) where LTRIM(RTRIM(SBU)) ='165'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: this lookup is to get data from SAS_HBISP_CANADA
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SAS_HBISP_CANADA1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT LTRIM(RTRIM(Style_group)) as Style_group, LTRIM(RTRIM(SBU)) as SBU, LTRIM(RTRIM(Customer)) as Customer, LTRIM(RTRIM(Currency)) as Currency FROM dbo.SAS_HBISP_CANADA with (nolock) where LTRIM(RTRIM(SBU)) ='15'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: this expression is to get records loaded before target
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_SAS_load

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF( I_SBU_ID='165' and V_SAS_STYLE_GRP ='X' AND V_SAS_CURRENCY = LTRIM(RTRIM(CURRENCY)) ,'Y', IIF ( I_SBU_ID='15' and lkp_Customer='X' AND lkpCurrency1 = LTRIM(RTRIM(CURRENCY)) ,'Y', IIF(CURRENCY ='USD' AND ISNULL(lkp_Customer) AND ISNULL(V_SAS_STYLE_GRP), 'Y' , 'N')))
--IIF( --V_SAS_STYLE_GRP ='X' AND V_SAS_CURRENCY = LTRIM(RTRIM(CURRENCY)) and lkp_Customer='X' AND lkpCurrency1 = LTRIM(RTRIM(CURRENCY)) ,'Y', --IIF(CURRENCY ='USD' AND ISNULL(lkp_Customer) AND ISNULL(V_SAS_STYLE_GRP), 'Y' , --'N'))
--IIF(I_SBU_ID='165' OR I_SBU_ID='15' and --V_SAS_STYLE_GRP ='X' AND V_SAS_CURRENCY = LTRIM(RTRIM(CURRENCY)) and lkp_Customer='X' AND lkpCurrency1 = LTRIM(RTRIM(CURRENCY)) ,'CAD', --IIF(CURRENCY ='USD' AND ISNULL(lkp_Customer) AND ISNULL(V_SAS_STYLE_GRP), 'Y' , --'N'))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: FLAG

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression transformation to transform the incoming records and populate to target table,
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_VOL_STAGE_HSF

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
I_FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY
--IIF(IN(FORECAST_TYPE, 'TRD_PRICE_SPEND', 'TRD_PROMO_SPEND', 'TRD_OOP','RG_TOT_ROY_EXP','NR_TOT_ROY_EXP'),FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY, --IIF(SAMBA_TANSFORMING_SIGN ='+' AND FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY<0, FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY *-1, --IIF (SAMBA_TANSFORMING_SIGN ='-' AND FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY>0 , FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY * -1, --- FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY --)))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_AMT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This retrieves the corresponding value from ESSBASE_SUB_VARS for the subvar_name.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ESSBASE_SUB_VARS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT essbase_sub_var.value as value, essbase_sub_var.variable as variable FROM essbase_sub_var with(nolock) where essbase_sub_var.application='HBISP' and essbase_sub_var.variable in ('cur_op_plan', 'cur_cust_plan')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: THE SOURCE QUALIFER TO FETCH RECORDS FROM FCST_SALES_FORECAST AND HSF_BATCH.FCST_XRF_SAMBA_MEASURE B
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_FCST_SALES_FORECAST

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID, A.FCST_STYLE_GROUP_KEY, TRIM(A.FCST_CPG_CODE), A.FISCAL_YEAR, A.FISCAL_PERIOD, TO_NUMBER(B.SAMBA_TANSFORMING_SIGN )* A.FORECAST_TYPE_QUANTITY, A.UPDATE_TIMESTAMP , B.SAMBA_MEASURE_ID, B.SAMBA_UOM , B.SAMBA_CLASSIFICATION, A.FORECAST_TYPE, A.CURRENCY FROM FCST_SALES_FORECAST A LEFT JOIN FCST_XRF_SAMBA_MEASURE B ON A.FORECAST_TYPE= B.SAS_MEASURE_ID WHERE B.SAMBA_MEASURE_ID IS NOT NULL
